--HOW TO BUILD--

The library depends on CMake, SDL, SDL_mixer and Magick++

To build the library and the examples:

cd tuxcap-build
cmake ../tuxcap
make

--INSTALL--

to install the shared library in /usr/local/lib

make install



Hack on!

Cheers,
W.P.
